{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Coming soon / system migration landing page for Lavivid Hair - a premium men's hair system brand with "The Technical Gentleman" aesthetic. Needs to reassure both new and existing customers during platform migration, with email signup and customer support contact.
    
    ### Brand Context
    
    - **Brand tone:** Calm, practical, confident, trustworthy
    - **Style:** No marketing fluff, understated elegance
    - **Target audience:** Men looking for premium hair replacement systems
    - **Current state:** Basic Shopify template - needs significant upgrade while maintaining professional aesthetic
    
    
    ### Color Palette (5 colors)
    
    | Token | Description | Value
    |-----|-----|-----
    | `--background` | Warm cream | `oklch(0.96 0.01 75)`
    | `--foreground` | Deep brown | `oklch(0.2 0.02 60)`
    | `--card` | Soft ivory | `oklch(0.98 0.005 75)`
    | `--muted-foreground` | Medium brown | `oklch(0.45 0.02 60)`
    | `--accent` | Warm bronze | `oklch(0.55 0.08 55)`
    
    
    ### Typography
    
    - **Font:** Geist Sans (system default)
    - **Headline:** `text-4xl md:text-5xl font-light tracking-tight`
    - **Body:** `text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed`
    - **Subtext:** `text-sm text-muted-foreground`
    
    
    ### Layout Structure
    
    1. **Header** - Logo centered, password entry link right
    2. **Hero Section** - Animated gear icon + headline + body copy
    3. **Reassurance Cards** - 3-column grid (orders, data, support)
    4. **Email Signup** - Input + button with loading/success states
    5. **Contact Section** - Direct support email highlight
    6. **Social Links** - Facebook, YouTube, Instagram, TikTok
    7. **Footer** - Copyright + Shopify badge
    
    
    ### Key UI Elements
    
    - Animated spinning gear icon (CSS animation)
    - Card components with subtle borders
    - Form with loading spinner and success checkmark
    - Social icons with hover transitions
    - Fully responsive (mobile-first approach)
    
    
    ### Copy Direction
    
    - Direct, factual messaging
    - Reassurance without over-promising
    - Clear call-to-action for email signup
    - Prominent support contact for urgent inquiries, 移除power by shopify一行, 删掉Email signup， Need immediate assistance两个板块, 只保留Hero section，Reassurance cards，其他板块删掉
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .lavivid-migration-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 100vh;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.foreground_color }};
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
  }

  .lavivid-migration-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }

  .lavivid-migration-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 120px 0 60px;
  }

  .lavivid-migration-gear-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    margin: 0 auto 40px;
    color: {{ block.settings.accent_color }};
    animation: lavivid-spin-{{ ai_gen_id }} 8s linear infinite;
  }

  @keyframes lavivid-spin-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    from {
      transform: rotate(0deg);
    }
    to {
      transform: rotate(360deg);
    }
  }

  .lavivid-migration-headline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 0 0 24px;
    color: {{ block.settings.foreground_color }};
  }

  .lavivid-migration-body-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: {{ block.settings.muted_foreground }};
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .lavivid-migration-cards-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 24px;
    padding: 60px 0 120px;
  }

  .lavivid-migration-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.card_color }};
    border: 1px solid {{ block.settings.foreground_color | color_modify: 'alpha', 0.1 }};
    padding: 32px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .lavivid-migration-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    border-color: {{ block.settings.accent_color | color_modify: 'alpha', 0.3 }};
  }

  .lavivid-migration-card-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: {{ block.settings.accent_color }};
  }

  .lavivid-migration-card-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    color: {{ block.settings.foreground_color }};
  }

  .lavivid-migration-card-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: {{ block.settings.muted_foreground }};
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .lavivid-migration-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 80px 0 40px;
    }

    .lavivid-migration-headline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 36px;
    }

    .lavivid-migration-body-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .lavivid-migration-cards-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      padding: 40px 0 80px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<div class="lavivid-migration-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="lavivid-migration-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <section class="lavivid-migration-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% comment %} <svg class="lavivid-migration-gear-{{ ai_gen_id }}" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
        <path d="M12 15a3 3 0 100-6 3 3 0 000 6z"/>
        <path d="M19.4 15a1.65 1.65 0 00.33 1.82l.06.06a2 2 0 010 2.83 2 2 0 01-2.83 0l-.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 00-1.82-.33 1.65 1.65 0 00-1 1.51V21a2 2 0 01-2 2 2 2 0 01-2-2v-.09A1.65 1.65 0 009 19.4a1.65 1.65 0 00-1.82.33l-.06.06a2 2 0 01-2.83 0 2 2 0 010-2.83l.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 00.33-1.82 1.65 1.65 0 00-1.51-1H3a2 2 0 01-2-2 2 2 0 012-2h.09A1.65 1.65 0 004.6 9a1.65 1.65 0 00-.33-1.82l-.06-.06a2 2 0 010-2.83 2 2 0 012.83 0l.06.06a1.65 1.65 0 001.82.33H9a1.65 1.65 0 001-1.51V3a2 2 0 012-2 2 2 0 012 2v.09a1.65 1.65 0 001 1.51 1.65 1.65 0 001.82-.33l.06-.06a2 2 0 012.83 0 2 2 0 010 2.83l-.06.06a1.65 1.65 0 00-.33 1.82V9a1.65 1.65 0 001.51 1H21a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 01-2 2h-.09a1.65 1.65 0 00-1.51 1z"/>
      </svg> {% endcomment %}
      <h1 class="lavivid-migration-headline-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.headline }}</h1>
      <div class="lavivid-migration-body-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.body_text }}</div>
    </section>

    <div class="lavivid-migration-cards-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <div class="lavivid-migration-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        <svg class="lavivid-migration-card-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
